'''肝醣儲積症'''（{{lang-en|Glycogen storage disease}}）屬於一種合成、分解[[肝醣|肝醣]]有缺陷的[[代謝疾病|代謝疾病]]<ref>{{DorlandsDict|nine/100012620|glycogen storage disease}}</ref>。另外，肝醣只分布於[[肝臟|肝臟]]、[[肌肉|肌肉]]。造成肝醣儲積症的病症有兩種，即先天與後天。先天型肝醣儲積症是因為出生前代謝系統出現問題（例如有缺陷的[[酵素|酵素]]）；在[[家畜|家畜]]之中，後天型肝醣儲積症是因為有毒的[[生物鹼|生物鹼]][[栗精胺|栗精胺]]所造成的<ref name="pmid7604496">{{cite journal
| author = Stegelmeier BL, Molyneux RJ, Elbein AD, James LF| title = The lesions of locoweed (Astragalus mollissimus), swainsonine, and castanospermine in rats| journal = Veterinary Pathology| volume = 32| issue = 3| pages = 289–98| pmid = 7604496| doi = 10.1177/03009858950320031 | url = | issn = | accessdate = 2009-05-15|date=May 1995}}</ref>。

整體而言，在[[不列顛哥倫比亞|不列顛哥倫比亞]]的調查顯示，肝醣儲積症發生率約為每10萬名嬰兒中會有2.3位，即每43000個嬰兒中有1位<ref name=BC>{{cite journal |author=Applegarth DA, Toone JR, Lowry RB |title=Incidence of inborn errors of metabolism in British Columbia, 1969-1996 |journal=Pediatrics |volume=105 |issue=1 |pages=e10 |pmid=10617747 |doi= 10.1542/peds.105.1.e10|url=|date=January 2000}}</ref>；在[[美國|美國]]的調查顯示約20000至25000名嬰兒中會有一人患有肝醣儲積症<ref name=Roth>[http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/949937-overview eMedicine Specialties > Glycogen-Storage Disease Type I] {{Wayback|url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/949937-overview |date=20171206155524 }} Author: Karl S Roth. Updated: Aug 31, 2009</ref>；而在[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]的發生率約為40000為嬰兒中有1位<ref name=Ausems>{{cite journal |author=Ausems MG, Verbiest J, Hermans MP, ''et al.'' |title=Frequency of glycogen storage disease type II in The Netherlands: implications for diagnosis and genetic counselling |journal=Eur. J. Hum. Genet. |volume=7 |issue=6 |pages=713–6 |pmid=10482961 |doi=10.1038/sj.ejhg.5200367 |url=|date=September 1999}}</ref>。

==類型==
[[File:Glycogen_storage_disease_in_liver_-_high_mag.jpg|left]]圖片，組織為肝臟活體切片，這個肝醣儲積症的類型是克里氏症，又稱為第三型肝醣儲積症，使用[[H&E染色法|H&E染色法]]。]]
目前肝醣儲積症可分為11大類(有一部份是過去被認為不同但現在已經重新分類)，肝醣合成缺乏症雖然不會造成額外的肝醣堆積，卻經常被稱為第零型肝醣儲積症，因為算是肝醣儲存缺陷的問題。

*第八型肝醣儲積症：過去被認為是一項獨立的肝醣代謝的疾病<ref name="pmid4508182">{{cite journal |author=Ludwig M, Wolfson S, Rennert O |title=Glycogen storage disease, type 8 |journal=Arch. Dis. Child. |volume=47 |issue=255 |pages=830–3 |pmid=4508182 |pmc=1648209 |doi= 10.1136/adc.47.255.830|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-disease-in-childhood_1972-10_47_255/page/830|date=October 1972}}</ref>，現在歸類到第六型肝醣儲積症<ref name="urleMedicine - Glycogen-Storage Disease Type VI : Article by Lynne Ierardi-Curto">{{cite web |url=http://www.emedicine.com/ped/TOPIC2564.HTM |title=eMedicine - Glycogen-Storage Disease Type VI : Article by Lynne Ierardi-Curto |format= |work= |accessdate= |archive-date=2008-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081031064619/http://www.emedicine.com/ped/TOPIC2564.HTM |dead-url=no }}</ref>，屬於[[X染色體|X染色體]]的[[隱性遺傳|隱性遺傳]]<ref name="urlDefinition: glycogen storage disease type VIII from Online Medical Dictionary">{{cite web |url=http://cancerweb.ncl.ac.uk/cgi-bin/omd?glycogen+storage+disease+type+VIII |title=Definition: glycogen storage disease type VIII from Online Medical Dictionary |format= |work= |accessdate=}}</ref>。

*第十型肝醣儲積症：過去也被認為是一項獨立的肝醣代謝的疾病<ref name="pmid6940112">{{cite journal |author=Warren MF, Hamilton PB |title=Glycogen storage disease type X caused by ochratoxin A in broiler chickens |journal=Poult. Sci. |volume=60 |issue=1 |pages=120–3 |pmid=6940112 |doi= |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_poultry-science_1981-01_60_1/page/120|date=January 1981}}</ref><ref name="pmid760630">{{cite journal |author=Huff WE, Doerr JA, Hamilton PB |title=Decreased glycogen mobilization during ochratoxicosis in broiler chickens |journal=Appl. Environ. Microbiol. |volume=37 |issue=1 |pages=122–6 |pmid=760630 |pmc=243410 |doi= |url=http://aem.asm.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=760630 |date=January 1979 |access-date=2011-10-25 |archive-date=2019-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218222836/https://aem.asm.org/content/37/1/122.long |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但現在也被歸類到第六型肝醣儲積症<ref name="urleMedicine - Glycogen-Storage Disease Type VI : Article by Lynne Ierardi-Curto">{{cite web |url=http://www.emedicine.com/ped/TOPIC2564.HTM |title=eMedicine - Glycogen-Storage Disease Type VI : Article by Lynne Ierardi-Curto |format= |work= |accessdate=}}</ref>。
